tileJSON.name: Protomaps Basemap
tileJSON.pgf:devanagari:name: NotoSansDevanagari-Regular

tileJSON.generator_options: tippecanoe -Z14 -z16 -B16 '--projection=EPSG:4326' -o ./data/output/pmtiles/places.mbtiles -l places ./data/output/geojson/places.geojson --force; tippecanoe -Z0 -z16 '--projection=EPSG:4326' -o ./data/output/pmtiles/admins.mbtiles -l admins --detect-shared-borders --drop-smallest-as-needed ./data/output/geojson/admins.geojson --force; tippecanoe -Z13 -z16 '--projection=EPSG:4326' -o ./data/output/pmtiles/buildings.mbtiles -l buildings --detect-shared-borders --drop-smallest-as-needed ./data/output/geojson/buildings.geojson --force; tippecanoe -Z5 -z16 -o ./data/output/pmtiles/roads.mbtiles -l roads --detect-shared-borders --drop-smallest-as-needed --coalesce-smallest-as-needed -j '{ "*": [ "any", [ "in", "class", "motorway" ], [ "all", [ ">=", "$zoom", 9 ], [ "in", "class", "primary", "secondary" ]],  [ "all", [ ">=", "$zoom", 11 ], [ "in", "class", "tertiary", "residential", "livingStreet" ]], [ ">=", "$zoom", 12]] }' -l roads ./data/output/geojson/roads.geojson --force; tile-join -pk -o ./data/output/pmtiles/overture.mbtiles ./data/output/pmtiles/admins.mbtiles ./data/output/pmtiles/roads.mbtiles ./data/output/pmtiles/buildings.mbtiles ./data/output/pmtiles/places.mbtiles --force
tileJSON.name: ./data/output/pmtiles/places.mbtiles + ./data/output/pmtiles/admins.mbtiles + ./data/output/pmtiles/buildings.mbtiles + ./data/output/pmtiles/roads.mbtiles
